    <content type="html">https://commandtree.dev/%3Ch1%20id=%22introducing-commandtree%22%20tabindex=%22-1%22%3E%3Ca%20class=%22header-anchor%22%20href=%22#introducing-commandtree%22%3EIntroducing%20CommandTree%3C/a%3E%3C/h1%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20project%20accumulates%20scripts.%20Shell%20scripts%20in%20%3Ccode%3Escripts/%3C/code%3E,%20npm%20scripts%20in%20%3Ccode%3Epackage.json%3C/code%3E,%20Makefile%20targets,%20VS%20Code%20tasks,%20launch%20configurations,%20Python%20scripts.%20They%20scatter%20across%20your%20project%20like%20leaves%20in%20autumn.%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommandTree%20gathers%20them%20all%20into%20one%20place.%3C/strong%3E%3C/p%3E%3Ch2%20id=%22the-problem%22%20tabindex=%22-1%22%3E%3Ca%20class=%22header-anchor%22%20href=%22#the-problem%22%3EThe%20Problem%3C/a%3E%3C/h2%3E%3Cp%3EYou&#39;re%20working%20on%20a%20project.%20You%20need%20to%20run%20the%20build%20script.%20Was%20it%20%3Ccode%3Enpm%20run%20build%3C/code%3E?%20Or%20was%20there%20a%20Makefile%20target?%20Maybe%20there&#39;s%20a%20shell%20script%20in%20%3Ccode%3Escripts/build.sh%3C/code%3E?%20You%20open%20the%20terminal,%20type%20%3Ccode%3Els%20scripts/%3C/code%3E,%20check%20%3Ccode%3Epackage.json%3C/code%3E,%20look%20at%20the%20Makefile...%3C/p%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shouldn&#39;t%20be%20hard.%3C/p%3E%3Ch2%20id=%22the-solution%22%20tabindex=%22-1%22%3E%3Ca%20class=%22header-anchor%22%20href=%22#the-solution%22%3EThe%20Solution%3C/a%3E%3C/h2%3E%3Cp%3EInstall%20CommandTree%20and%20a%20new%20panel%20appears%20in%20your%20VS%20Code%20sidebar.%20Every%20runnable%20task%20in%20your%20workspace%20is%20right%20there,%20categorized%20and%20ready%20to%20go:%3C/p%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShell%20scripts%20(%3Ccode%3E.sh%3C/code%3E,%20%3Ccode%3E.bash%3C/code%3E,%20%3Ccode%3E.zsh%3C/code%3E)%3C/li%3E%3Cli%3ENPM%20scripts%20from%20every%20%3Ccode%3Epackage.json%3C/code%3E%3C/li%3E%3Cli%3EMakefile%20targets%3C/li%3E%3Cli%3EVS%20Code%20tasks%20from%20%3Ccode%3Etasks.json%3C/code%3E%3C/li%3E%3Cli%3ELaunch%20configurations%20from%20%3Ccode%3Elaunch.json%3C/code%3E%3C/li%3E%3Cli%3EPython%20scripts%3C/li%3E%3C/ul%3E%3Cp%3EClick%20the%20play%20button.%20Done.%3C/p%3E%3Ch2%20id=%22quick-tasks%22%20tabindex=%22-1%22%3E%3Ca%20class=%22header-anchor%22%20href=%22#quick-tasks%22%3EQuick%20Tasks%3C/a%3E%3C/h2%3E%3Cp%3EPin%20your%20favorites.%20Click%20the%20star%20icon%20on%20any%20task%20and%20it%20appears%20in%20the%20Quick%20Tasks%20panel%20at%20the%20top.%20Your%20most-used%20commands%20are%20always%20one%20click%20away.%3C/p%3E%3Ch2%20id=%22tags-and-filters%22%20tabindex=%22-1%22%3E%3Ca%20class=%22header-anchor%22%20href=%22#tags-and-filters%22%3ETags%20and%20Filters%3C/a%3E%3C/h2%3E%3Cp%3EGroup%20related%20tasks%20with%20tags.%20Filter%20the%20tree%20by%20text%20or%20tag.%20Find%20exactly%20what%20you%20need,%20instantly.%3C/p%3E%3Ch2%20id=%22get-started%22%20tabindex=%22-1%22%3E%3Ca%20class=%22header-anchor%22%20href=%22#get-started%22%3EGet%20Started%3C/a%3E%3C/h2%3E%3Cp%3EInstall%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href=%22https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=nimblesite.commandtree%22%3EVS%20Code%20Marketplace%3C/a%3E%20or%20from%20source:%3C/p%3E%3Cpre%20class=%22language-bash%22%3E%3Ccode%20class=%22language-bash%22%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22token%20function%22%3Enpm%3C/span%3E%20%3Cspan%20class=%22token%20function%22%3Einstall%3C/span%3E%3Cspan%20class=%22token%20function%22%3Enpm%3C/span%3E%20run%20packagecode%20--install-extension%20commandtree-*.vsix%3C/code%3E%3C/pre%3E%3Cp%3EOpen%20any%20workspace%20and%20CommandTree%20does%20the%20rest.%3C/p%3E</content>
    
